# Tickets utilisateur

Voici la liste des champs que le post-only voit : 

* title
* description
* type
* status
* category
* last update
* Time to own
* Time to resolve
* Internal time to own
* Internal time to resolve
* Request source
* urgency
* Approval
* Impact
* priority
* Location
* requester
* Watcher
* Assigned to
* Linked tickets
* documents
* followups
* Statistics (tab)
* items
* history


Voici la liste des champs que le post-only peut modifier : 

* title
* description
* category
* urgency
* documents
* followups
* items





Informations a mettre sur les vignettes post-only

* id
* titre
* priority 		=> color / icon   => https://image.flaticon.com/icons/svg/829/829545.svg ou sur une ligne https://image.flaticon.com/icons/svg/60/60839.svg or https://i.redd.it/nz01doblh6g01.jpg
* time to resolve	=> icon / chart
* status		=> icon / color
* last update
* number followups
* type			=> icon
* approval		=> color / icon






type : 

* incident : ambulance
* request  : avion en papier

couleurs de fond : 
* bleu = nouveau, en cours, planifie
* gris clair  = en attente
* vert = resole / clos





# Dahboards

## Admin

* tasks / planning
* nb tickets by due time (overdue, today, tomorrow, this week, next week)
* number assets
* task fusion (deploy...)


## Technician

* tasks / planning
* tickets assigned to me
* tickets assigned to my groups
* nb tickets by due time (overdue, today, tomorrow, this week, next week)


## Supervisor

* Tickets after end SLA
* tickets near to end SLA
* stats like number tickets in last days per days
* stats like number tickets per hour in last 24 hours
* tickets by type (demande / incident)


